image_analysis.description: A high-angle photograph of a desk setup. The desk surface is a bright teal/turquoise color. On the desk, there is a large Apple iMac computer, a black wireless keyboard resting on top of an 'AT-A-GLANCE' desk calendar, a black mouse on a mousepad, and several personal items including framed photographs, a tissue box, a small decorative green tree, and a pencil holder. In the background, a living room area with dark furniture and white sofas is visible. A lamp with a tan shade is on the left side of the desk.
image_analysis.layout: The desk occupies the foreground and midground, with a living room visible in the background.
